<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-61-0701 </DOCNO><TEXT>The function of the monitoring systems is to acquire, to process and tostore the necessary data and to provide the supporting methods and toolsallowing a safe analysis. The paper describes such information systemsexemplified by monitoring systems for loose parts, vibrations and fatigue.Advanced micro processor systems allow to match detection criteria tothe latest state of knowledge and experience by modifying the softwarewithout interfering with the hardware.</TEXT></DOC>